    • Field Detail

      • FILES_PER_FOLDER

        public static final int FILES_PER_FOLDER
        File organization of file stores. There are 2 levels of sub folders in the temp dir, each folder contains 1000 sub folders or files (in the leaf folders). A file store file is then located in, e.g. <filestore_dir>/000/000/000/file1.bin
